{"tid":1219641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人集資邀請話反送中有錢收嘅廢老 企最前做肉盾","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T01:26:51.000Z","uid":4352,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0eca9d7830bfd5cee3c0f82f43b76ddab798a71","tid":1219641,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:09:40.000Z","msg":"成日話有錢收<br />\n底價俾3000佢<br />\n同佢講要企前排 絕大機會俾狗打及拘捕<br />\n咁多錢收實肯做啦<br />\n收到錢又可以返大陸玩<br />\n絕對唔洗擔心佢地體力<br />\n知道香港排隊黨有5-6成都係班廢老<br />\n連續企同曬五六個鐘都無事<br />\n同埋佢地稱年輕人捱唔到苦<br />\n佢地嘅意志力一定更強<br />\n催淚彈？布袋彈？實彈佢地都中過啦<br />\n<br />\n唔洗外國僱傭兵<br />\n佢地已經係最強僱傭兵<br />\n係佢地眼中咩都係為錢<br />\n有錢就咩都得<br />\n所以為咗提升防禦力 <br />\n集資邀請佢地做肉盾真係一個好方法<br />\n但唔洗佢地叫口號<br />\n因為佢地實叫錯<br />\n正係企前面推就得"},{"pid":"38a506961d585df6fba718355ab8cb3b12953909","tid":1219641,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"另外有無人識網上媒體<br />\n平時佢地搵年輕人做街訪<br />\n今次搵下廢中廢老做<br />\n問下佢地收幾錢肯出黎俾人打俾人拉"},{"pid":"01fc2c40840e1184103b1853e12be9f330afcad3","tid":1219641,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:11:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bde2485e5c595d41bd788a486e1b01795971471","tid":1219641,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:12:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea6658fd3638aa2d8eb63df2422553ed717b32cc","tid":1219641,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b71c0f879d0f997075880c032d01daf8efded161","tid":1219641,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:12:27.000Z","msg":"幫推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc56f36f7b2162ea6d7bf1a2fe481b86895db97","tid":1219641,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:12:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881ef4d5b1c4a5d493a31a6e8975f67f2